headline: Cathay Pacific To Purchase More GE Aerospace (GE) Engines To Power 777-9s
summary: GE Aerospace (NYSE:GE) is among the 11 Best Large Cap Defense Stocks to Buy According to Analysts. On August 6, the company announced that Cathay Pacific has signed an agreement to purchase more GE9X engines to power the 777-9 aircraft.
